<codeline lineno="80"><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/></highlight><highlight class="comment">//<sp/>TODO:<sp/>Direction<sp/>should<sp/>probably<sp/>be<sp/>transformed<sp/>as<sp/>well.</highlight><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="81"><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/>vector_t<sp/>normalized_direction{0.f,<sp/>0.f,<sp/>0.f,<sp/>1.f};</highlight></codeline>
